# Data Structures

## Offer Image Base (object)

+ original: `https://www.kangaroorewards.com/photos/image.png` (string)
+ large: `https://www.kangaroorewards.com/photos/image1.png` (string)
+ medium: `https://www.kangaroorewards.com/photos/image1.png` (string)
+ thumbnail: `https://www.kangaroorewards.com/photos/image1.png` (string)

## UploadOfferImageData (object)

+ image_original: `https://www.kangaroorewards.com/photos/image.png` (string) - A binary file. (up to 10MB)
+ image_large: `https://www.kangaroorewards.com/photos/image1.png` (string) - A binary file. (up to 1MB)
+ image_medium: `https://www.kangaroorewards.com/photos/image1.png` (string) - A binary file. (up to 512KB)
+ image_thumbnail: `https://www.kangaroorewards.com/photos/image1.png` (string) - A binary file. (up to 256KB)
